242
00:26:11,600 --> 00:26:16,600
 "Moram činiti dijela očeva."

243
00:26:16,600 --> 00:26:28,600
 Sjetite se koliko smo bili svjesni

244
00:26:28,600 --> 00:26:31,600
 Božje ljubavi prošle godine, očeve ljubavi.

245
00:26:31,600 --> 00:26:37,600
 Otac je taj koji šalje Isusa

246
00:26:37,600 --> 00:26:41,600
