 Sve.

690
00:57:18,600 --> 00:57:22,600
 Stavljam u tvoje ruke.

691
00:57:22,600 --> 00:57:25,600
 stavljam po tvoje noge.

692
00:57:25,600 --> 00:57:35,600
 To znači imati Isusa kao gospodina u svom životu.

693
00:57:35,600 --> 00:57:41,600
 To je ogroman skok za velik broj ljudi.

694
00:57:41,600 --> 00:57:45,600
 A moram reći posebno za muškarce.

695
00:57:45,600 --> 00:57:52,600
 Mi ne volimo bilo kome povjeravati svoj život.

696
00:57:52,600 --> 00:57:55,600
 Ja sam muško.

697
00:57:55,600 --> 00:57:58,600
 Ja se brinem o sebi.

698
00:57:58,600 --> 00:58:01,600
 Ja se brinem o svojoj obitelji.

699
00:58:01,600 --> 00:58:04,600
 To je moj posao.

700
00:58:04,600 --> 00:58:08,600
 Da, to je tvoj posao.

701
00:58:08,600 --> 00:58:12,600
 ali je i njegov posao.

702
00:58:12,600 --> 00:58:17,600
 Ali što bi on htio učiniti

703
00:58:17,600 --> 00:58:24,600
 je da ti radiš pod njegovim autoritetom.

704
00:58:24,600 --> 00:58:28,600
 Pod njegovom snagom.

705
00:58:28,600 --> 00:58:33,600
 Pod njegovim savjetom i upravljanjem.

706
00:58:33,600 --> 00:58:43,600
 Nećeš učiniti da staviš svoju obitelj pod njegovom gospodstvom.

707
00:58:43,600 --> 00:58:46,600
 A onda kažeš: Oda ja, više ne trebam ovdje.

708
00:58:46,600 --> 00:58:50,600
 I dalje imaš svoje odgovornosti.

709
00:58:50,600 --> 00:58:58,600
 A sada i dijeliš sa nekime ko stvarno može napraviti razliku.

710
00:58:58,600 --> 00:59:01,600
 Braćo, jako sam ozbiljan.

711
00:59:01,600 --> 00:59:08,600
 Ovo je dostupno svima u ovoj sobi večeras.

712
00:59:08,600 --> 00:59:23,600
 I to je pitanje na koje svaki čovjek treba odgovoriti.

713
00:59:23,600 --> 00:59:27,600
 Mogu li mu vjerovati?

714
00:59:27,600 --> 00:59:32,600
 Postoji jedna prekrasna priča o Bibliji.

715
00:59:32,600 --> 00:59:40,600
 Bio je čovjek čiji je sin imao puno problema.

716
00:59:40,600 --> 00:59:47,600
 I molio je Isusa da mu ozdravi sina.

717
00:59:47,600 --> 00:59:52,600
 I čovjek kaže Isusu:

718
00:59:52,600 --> 01:00:01,600
 Ako možeš nešto učiniti, molim te učini.

719
01:00:01,600 --> 01:00:06,600
 Isus mu malo pokaže stav.

720
01:00:06,600 --> 01:00:11,600
 Ako mogu nešto učiniti?

721
01:00:11,600 --> 01:00:15,600
 Ako mogu nešto učiniti?

722
01:00:15,600 --> 01:00:22,600
 čovjek čovjek čovjek da izgovara najljepšu rečenicu u Bibliji.

723
01:00:22,600 --> 01:00:27,600
 Gospodine, vjerujem.

724
01:00:27,600 --> 01:00:33,600
 Pomozi mojoj nevjeri.

725
01:00:33,600 --> 01:00:37,600
 Napravit ćemo jedan brzi test.

726
01:00:37,600 --> 01:00:39,600
 Hvala što je učiniti?

727
01:00:39,600 --> 01:00:41,600
 Ako mogu nešto učiniti, da je učiniti?

728
01:00:41,600 --> 01:00:43,600
 Ako mogu nešto učiniti, da je učiniti?

729
01:00:43,600 --> 01:00:44,600
 Dignite ruke.

730
01:00:44,600 --> 01:00:46,600
 Ako vjeruješ u Boga, digni ruke.

731
01:00:46,600 --> 01:00:48,600
 Ako vjeruješ u Boga, digni ruke.

732
01:00:48,600 --> 01:00:50,600
 Spustite ruke.

733
01:00:50,600 --> 01:00:52,600
 Spustite ruke.

734
01:00:52,600 --> 01:00:57,600
 Svi dobri sveti ljudi koji vjerujete u Boga.

735
01:00:57,600 --> 01:01:00,600
 I include you.

736
01:01:00,600 --> 01:01:05,600
 How many men here in the last six months

737
01:01:05,600 --> 01:01:08,600
 have been worried or troubled about anything?

738
01:01:08,600 --> 01:01:09,600
 Could you just raise your hands?

739
01:01:09,600 --> 01:01:18,600
 What's your hand doing up?

740
01:01:18,600 --> 01:01:20,600
 What's my hand doing up?

741
01:01:20,600 --> 01:01:21,600
 Yeah.

742
01:01:21,600 --> 01:01:23,600
 Spustite ruke.

743
01:01:23,600 --> 01:01:26,600
 Brothers, can you see the mystery?

744
01:01:26,600 --> 01:01:28,600
 Can you see the mystery?

745
01:01:28,600 --> 01:01:33,600
 We're ready to die for Jesus.

746
01:01:33,600 --> 01:01:38,600
 And yet, we struggle with our own doubts and fears.

747
01:01:38,600 --> 01:01:43,600
 That does not disqualify us.

748
01:01:43,600 --> 01:01:47,600
 That should show us how more we need to come

749
01:01:47,600 --> 01:01:49,600
 to seek his guidance and direction.

750
01:01:49,600 --> 01:01:52,600
 To nam samo pokazuje koliko više moramo ići

751
01:01:52,600 --> 01:01:55,600
 i tražiti njegov osmjerenje i njegov sabit.

752
01:01:55,600 --> 01:01:58,600
